  "title": "Product Design & R&D Director",
  "description": "<p><strong>【Job Advertisement | Product Design &amp; R&amp;D Director】</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Position:</strong> Product Design &amp; R&amp;D Director<br>\n <strong>Salary Range:</strong> SGD 7,000 – 9,000 / month<br>\n <strong>Location:</strong> Singapore</p>\n<p>We are seeking a highly creative and visionary <strong>Product Design &amp; R&amp;D Director</strong> to lead our design innovation and product development team. This role requires strong artistic sensitivity, strategic thinking, and the ability to transform concepts into market-leading products.</p>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead the product design and R&amp;D department, overseeing the full development cycle from concept to final production.</li>\n  <li>Create innovative, aesthetically appealing, and functional product designs with a strong sense of artistry.</li>\n  <li>Conduct market research and analyze industry trends to guide new product directions.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate closely with engineering, marketing, and production teams to ensure seamless execution.</li>\n  <li>Maintain and elevate the brand’s design language and product quality standards.</li>\n  <li>Manage and mentor the design team, ensuring continuous creativity and growth.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proven experience in product design, industrial design, or related fields.</li>\n  <li>Strong artistic sensibility and exceptional creativity.</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in design leadership or R&amp;D management roles.</li>\n  <li>Excellent understanding of materials, manufacturing processes, and product aesthetics.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and project management skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to lead multiple projects simultaneously in a fast-paced environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Opportunity to lead design innovation in a rapidly growing company.</li>\n  <li>Creative working environment with strong support for new ideas.</li>\n  <li>Competitive salary package and career advancement prospects.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are passionate about design, innovation, and artistic expression, we welcome your application.</p>",
